at it accomplishes your methodology conclusions and the implications of your work this may take more than one paragraph but you should write to a general audience as opposed to specialists in your field discuss future plans for research or research interest as well you should also point out supporting fields in which you have expertise or enumerate the variety of classes you could teach if the position requires teaching be enthusiastic about your experience and discuss the courses you have developed and or your teaching style closing conclude and deal with logistics namely what materials you have enclosed eg cv research statement teaching portfolio writing samples etc and will send separately letters of recommendation mention that you look forward to meeting with the search committee in an interview and let them know how they can contact you email cell phone back to top sample cover letters up sample academic cover letters groups career development center printer friendly version calendar schedule an appointment graphic calendar pages schedule an appointment with a career counselor quick links calendar career fair schedule career planning handbook career library vault guided career path facebook linkedin what is the cdc copyright 2011 stanford university terms of use copyright complaints report a problem with this site
